Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.11,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We made it to Venice! {Line 2 and 3 are the same as Episode 18 -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.65,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm diving into the canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.38,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista! \NGet out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:38.01,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,G-Giorno! \NY-You're... already starting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:44.27,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,As I'm sure you're aware, Mista,\Nour top priority is to retrieve the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Our success lies in its retrieval!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.78,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The disc is right inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.74,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Since we're surrounded by such a large body of water, \Nit will take longer for him to freeze the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's why I did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.95,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me! \NHurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:04.83,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I hear you, Giorno!\NBut your idea of success doesn't do it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:09.09,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Killing him, then the two of us\Ngetting what we came here for... {Totally fine if you want to revert, I just hate "the object" -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.30,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.34,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Like fucking hell you'll get off that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.77,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Go right ahead and jump in, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:30.86,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll take my chances on whether or not\Nyou can outswim my ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.90,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,N-No! \NDriving into the canal was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:40.12,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The way he uses ice... is unbeatable!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
Comment: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:15.75,Title Part 5,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(402,394)\pos(107,923)\fs60}Episodio 19  White Album
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.46,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Turn the car into a plant, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.76,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The hood hasn't completely frozen up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.51,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So hurry up and grow some plants \Nwhile you can still create life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.69,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Trying to grow vines to use as ropes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.35,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fuck that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.90,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:42.57,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,As I thought, in order to make a vine that will grow fast enough to reach the bank, I need heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:47.62,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,At this temperature, only short grass \Nlike you'd find in a tundra can sustain life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.75,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Who said anything about using them\Nto reach the bank, Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This'll do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.67,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Short grass is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But I need more! More! A lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.55,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Keep making more if you wanna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.97,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We're gonna die if you don't hurry up, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.02,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Gotcha! \NSucks that it didn't grow to the bank of the canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.31,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You did it, Giorno!\N It froze over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.65,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Now you're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.82,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Th-That fucker! \NHe made me freeze the grass and turn it into a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.66,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,N-No... A snowboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.99,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Fucking dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.12,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He's not gonna let me off that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:32.83,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.38,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album! \NTemporarily unfreeze the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Th-The ice...{lol CR actually had "Th ice". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.38,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.02,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,This is the static world of sub zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.90,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Nothing can move at temperatures this low!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.56,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It fucks everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:02.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,That's why my White Album is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:07.07,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I could stop the whole fucking ocean if I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.58,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Hurry and reach the bank, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.83,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Gather up the grass floating in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.46,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The grass you were using as a snowboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.42,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Do it while you can still fire with your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.09,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just give up, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:28.85,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Don't you get that attacking me is fucking pointless?!{Oh my god, I know I said Ghiacchio is Dio now last week, but I didn't expect him to commit to that so quickly. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.23,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Gathering up grass... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:46.24,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno, if you release your ability, \Nthe short grass will turn back into car parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.99,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...which makes them perfect for attacking him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.24,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.96,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,D-Did that finish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.63,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,No, too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.67,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We only have a temporary reprieve from the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But Mista, you've bought us precious time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:12.14,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Let's quickly grab the object, then get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.56,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We won't be able to employ the same strategy\Nif he catches us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.73,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Please go, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:22.27,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The disc should show up somewhere\Nif I destroy the lion statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.82,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I'll snatch it and hide in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.57,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If I have a few dozen seconds, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.28,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,But will hiding be enough to lose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:34.37,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I think it will work, but I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.66,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Either way, this guy is seriously bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:42.42,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If he runs into Buccellati and the others... That would be the worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,We need to finish this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.22,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.84,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Wha...?! \NMista! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:53.30,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Your ability is perfect? Yeah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:58.52,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If you're totally encased in ice,\Nthen just how are you breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.36,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,That's it. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.07,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Air's leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.70,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He's breathing from a hole at the back of his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.12,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Get into position, Sex Pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:15.79,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Number One and Number Two, \Ngo around and flank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.00,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's lookin' right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.71,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's gonna use another ice attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.38,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,No, he's gonna go up for air first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.76,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Once he reaches the surface,\NI'm gonna fire right into his breathing hole!{Oops. A CR mistranslation that I missed the first time around. He says he'll "shove bullets into the hole", not "shoot a hole in his head". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.34,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's trying to surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.93,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Here we go, Pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.56,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,We have to time this for\N the instant he takes a breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.68,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.52,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Number One and Two say they can't see the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.36,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's how he's swimming! \NHe's looking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.98,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's hiding the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.07,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,O-Oh no! Let's scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.40,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.28,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Hold your position, \NNumber One and Number Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.54,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Did you seriously hit my fucking forehead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.58,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.63,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.92,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You shot at the fish swimming around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.59,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.51,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He looked down! We can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.09,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's the hole! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.85,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.40,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Hooray! Bullseye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.41,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Th-That noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.12,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That noise... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.91,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,So you found my breathing hole\Nand decided to target it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.71,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.50,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Too bad temperatures this low stop everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:52.17,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Gases turn to liquids, and liquids turn to solids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.89,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Get a good look. \NSee how there's no airflow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.43,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,The bullet, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.47,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's the sound of a ricocheting bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.27,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album: Gently Weeps! {https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bI8P6ZSHSvE}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.40,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.73,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I had already created a wall of frozen air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:18.66,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It uses up a good chunk of my Stand's power, \Nbut now you won't even be able to shoot a bolt into my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.16,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It stops anything that comes near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.75,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You're the one who made me learn my lesson, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.46,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Giorno was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.21,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This is all my fault... \NIt's my responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:35.26,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I should have focused on getting the object...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.60,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It's not under the trash can or bench...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:45.19,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Nothing that seems important,\Nand it's not like they'd hide it out in the open, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:51.40,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But based on how Mista was running around,\Nit must be somewhere it can be found quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.36,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Where is it? \NThis photo should be a hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.70,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is bad. \NOur situation is dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.08,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista's beginning to act out of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.29,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's decided to take full responsibility for this, \Neven at the cost of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:12.96,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,But only those who possess true resolve\Ncan forge a path through the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.55,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.38,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Self sacrifice will be necessary at worst,\Nbut if Mista and I share the responsibility for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.18,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,...our combined resolve will forge a path!
Comment: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.31,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It was in here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:34.03,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Hiding inside the statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.57,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:41.12,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,If I get close enough, \NI should be able to shoot another bullet into his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.95,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I just need to be able to aim through his wall of air...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.66,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista's become reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.92,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He's willing to take responsibility for this\Nat the cost of his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.17,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,But what we need isn't bravery \Nborn from being backed into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.55,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It's resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.30,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What we need right now is resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.51,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Resolve doesn't mean sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.80,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,A computer disc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.80,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.81,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You were looking for something\Nto lead you to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.90,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I fucking did it!\NNow we can go expose the boss's true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:14.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,All that's left now... is Trish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.57,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll take care of her after finishing you motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.11,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Come on! \NFight until you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.82,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll finish you assholes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.70,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.75,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:41.93,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Resolve is the ability to forge a path\Nthrough the darkest night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.43,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Guido Mista: Arrested at age seventeen for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.90,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The result of the trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:58.23,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His plea that he acted out of self-defense was rejected, and he was sentenced fifteen to thirty years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.24,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,My happy-go-lucky youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.03,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Is this really my fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:13.00,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Mista's outlook on life had always been optimistic, \Nbut at this moment, his head was buried in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.34,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.51,Flashback,Guard,0,0,0,,Get up. You're being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.98,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,You're the one who bailed me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:37.86,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw the incident on the news\Nand was convinced you acted out of self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:43.70,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,To keep it short, I see how passionate you are and know how skilled you are at gunslinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.62,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,But someone like you\Nwouldn't last two years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.33,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.41,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,You pulled some strings for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.29,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Are you part of some organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.08,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.96,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,There's an excellent ristorante nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.35,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,You have quite the appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:17.23,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,The bruschetta here is great, too. \NDo you still have room for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.27,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.98,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.57,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.03,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you get him some... \NActually, for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.03,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you get us four orders of bruschetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:29.87,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Actually, make that five. \NI'll have some, too, while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.58,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.46,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,So, to pick up where we left off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.54,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.13,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I think the two of us will get along great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.04,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,So count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:40.88,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,On one condition, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:45.30,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Treat me to some dolce, too.{And his master?} \N Does this place have strawberry cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.55,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,You're a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.60,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,I guess this is fate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.27,Flashback,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't so bad, I guess. \NEverything worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:05.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Mista learned that everyone's destiny is pre-determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:10.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Though people tend to stall \Nor take detours when they're young...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:15.29,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...they ultimately end up traveling\N the path they were destined to take.{Just confirming what Gyro was asking, yes, the Japanese phrasing here and on the previous line is 1=1 with episode 8. -Starfish}{As of the TV version, these three are all copied from 8 -T}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.34,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I see it! The path I need to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.21,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,This time I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.26,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It's there, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.72,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I can see the path I gotta take through the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.27,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:47.40,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You fuckheads just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.91,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The air is frozen because of how low the temperature is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.37,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:58.75,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,If I let air that's been frozen solid\Ninto my suit and let it melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.67,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,...it turns back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.67,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,If I take it in like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.96,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Just like a diver with an air tank strapped to their back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.80,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,...I don't need a breathing hole anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.18,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Th-The hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.18,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He deflected the bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.39,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,All six of 'em! O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:19.39,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You better have the fucking resolve for this, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.32,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.99,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Yeah, my resolve is there, Giorno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:34.16,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,If you hadn't given me your resolve, \NI wouldn't have seen this path....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.71,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve to take a path\Nwhere I'm willingly shot by my own bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.25,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I-I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.30,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The blood froze and hardened to my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.34,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,My path through the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:52.72,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...wasn't the one where my bullets\Npenetrated your wall of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:57.06,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I-It was the one where\NI splattered your face with my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.39,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Shit! I can't get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.02,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Hey, the metal pole from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.98,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista, your bullet shaped it into a{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.70,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Ow! That fucking hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:17.04,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Something... Something... Something... \NSomething warm is{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You asked me if I had the resolve for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.92,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, I'm about to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.67,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But you'll have to show some resolve of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:32.34,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve to be shot full of holes\Nand leave for the next world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.93,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Th-The fucker's still standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.10,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,He's hell-bent on shoving me further back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.56,Thoughts,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Is he fucking nuts?!\NHe's gonna push my neck into the spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.27,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Shit! I need to get this out of my neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.78,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're crazy! \NThe bullet's gonna come flying back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.70,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're not gonna last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.24,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I have to make it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.41,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This is my true resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.99,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Pistols, steel yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.96,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,White Album: Gently Weeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.93,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Y-You can't take any more, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.31,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.06,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,And that'll mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.35,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,...we'll die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.90,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,N-Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.94,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I'm still conscious! \NI can still shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.03,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Y-You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.83,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It went all the way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.74,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,You're... wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:47.04,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The one with stronger resolve... is me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.54,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Guido Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:55.80,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'll commend you for...\Ndriving me so far up against the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:18:00.51,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,But the one who took better advantage \Nof all the blood splatter... was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:05.14,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I froze the blood that spurted out of my neck\Nto keep me fixed in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.19,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Now my neck can't be\Npushed any farther into the spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.48,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I'm completely secured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.36,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The spike won't go any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.07,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Also... Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.70,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,The last bullet you shot is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.08,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Right in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.62,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.54,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,There's no wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.75,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.92,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:43.56,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Your resolve is illuminating the path, \Nshining even brighter than the rising sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.73,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,And it's shining on the path...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.81,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...that we're meant to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.19,Main,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,What the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:57.99,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:17.38,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Recently... I started noticing... that even though Giorno Giovanna... is so new at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:23.68,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,...things always seem...\Nto play out exactly how he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.39,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,The resolve I showed just now \Nwas also partly Giorno's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:31.73,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,It made its way into my heart\Nbefore I realized it had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.78,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He almost feels more like my capo than Buccellati does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.40,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He drove me to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.15,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,What's the deal with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.28,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Well, I guess now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.08,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,It's not my style to dwell on stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:53.46,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Mista, we safely retrieved the disc thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.09,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hurry up and heal me.\N I-I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:01.89,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have found that resolve\Nif I didn't have faith in your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.56,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hurry up and heal me before I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:10.31,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Of course. \NBut I need to make something clear to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Gold Experience's ability\Ndoesn't exactly have healing properties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.44,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It recreates parts of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:21.07,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,My plan is to imbue the bullets embedded in your body with life\Nand to plug up your arteries and other injured areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.03,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Just quit talking and do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.91,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Since I'm not exactly healing you, \Nyour pain will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Please don't complain to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.33,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:37.00,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,O-Oww! Be more gentle! \NJesus, be more gentle Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.76,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're a gangster for crying out loud, so quit fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:46.30,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You have about eighteen more wounds, \Nso you'll need to remove your clothes for me to take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.23,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Buccellati! \NI'm picking up two signals...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.40,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like there's anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.86,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.36,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I can only assume it's Mista and Giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:04.07,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,They must be bored out of their minds waiting for us\Nif it went so smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.53,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Ah! Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.16,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,There they are!\N Hey, Mista! Gio{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.49,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,{\an8}Be gentler! \NGentler, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.12,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Don't take off my clothes! \NI can't take it!
